      "layout": "The page primarily uses a full-bleed layout for the main content area, with a strong implied central axis for navigation elements. The hero section is characterized by centered textual content and prominent pixel-art icons. Sections are visually distinct through consistent vertical spacing (72px section gap) rather than alternating background bands. Content arrangement is typically centered or implicitly aligned, fostering a sense of balance. Navigation is provided via a minimalist top bar with pixel-icon links.",
